These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, vegafina, dunhill, aristoff, baccarat
House: cape-cod, victorian, ranch-style, colonial, palace
1. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
2. the colonial house is in the middle##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the siglo-smoker is between the colonial house and the ranch-style house##2
6. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
7. the colonial house is on the right of the palace house##1
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Cigar          | vegafina | siglo | baccarat | aristoff | dunhill |
| House   | ranch-style  | palace      | colonial   | cape-cod     | victorian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
5 different games are played: canasta, poker, scrabble, chess, mah-jongg
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, rock-climbing, camping, writing, photography
1. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Game   | scrabble     | chess       | mah-jongg    | canasta | poker   |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | woodworking | writing | photography      | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
City: venice, liverpool, paris, rome, boston
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bongani, game, bluemaster, swisher
1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person traveling to venice##1
2. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
5. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
6. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| City         | venice | paris | liverpool | rome    | boston |
| Cigar   | bluemaster     | dannemann        | game      | bongani | swisher      |

