.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
City: paris, prague, new-york, boston, rome
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, iris, daffodil, marigold, amaryllis
1. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to rome is the person who growsiris##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person traveling to prague is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person traveling to rome##2
7. the person who growsamaryllis is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| City         | paris      | boston | new-york | prague   | rome  |
| Flower   | marigold | amaryllis    | daffodil        | rose | iris |

