.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, lavender, lilac, brown, coral
5 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, cat, goldfish, goat
1. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
5. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes orange is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Color      | coral      | lavender | orange   | brown  | lilac  |
| Pet   | cat | goldfish | hamster | lizard | goat |

