.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, snowboarding, swimming, biathlon, climbing
House: colonial, wooden, craftsman, victorian, cape-cod
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
2. the wooden house is between the cape-cod house and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the wooden house##1
5. the craftsman house is the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
8. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Sport   | snowboarding        | tennis                | biathlon  | swimming  | climbing            |
| House        | colonial | cape-cod | wooden | craftsman | victorian |

