.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, drawing, magic-tricks, camping, photography
5 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish, mouse, chinchilla, rabbit
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Hobby   | photography       | magic-tricks   | drawing    | camping    | hiking |
| Pet        | mouse | fish | goldfish | rabbit | chinchilla     |

