.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, pink, blue, ivory, turquise
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, quad-bike, trike, subway
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Color      | blue  | coral       | pink      | ivory  | turquise   |
| Transport   | subway | helicopter | trike | bus | quad-bike |

