4. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching epic movies is the person who likes brown##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
8. the person who likes coral is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | epic | fantasy     | time-travel | satire |
| Color           | coral | brown     | black | ivory    | blood-red      |

