.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, horror, time-travel, scientific, disaster
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, german, argentine, colombian, egyptian
1. the german is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the egyptian is the person watching musical movies##1
3. the egyptian is in the middle##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
5. the german is on the far left or far right##3
6. the japanese is between the egyptian and the person watching horror movies##2
7. the german is in an odd position##4
8. the german is on the far left##1
9. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre        | scientific | disaster | musical  | time-travel | horror     |
| Nationality   | german  | argentine     | egyptian | japanese      | colombian |

