.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, dressmaker, musician, manager, software-developer
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping, sudoku, hiking, reading
1. the manager is in an even position##4
