3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
4. the manager is on the right of the dressmaker##1
5. the musician is in an even position##4
6. the dressmaker is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the musician##2
7. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Job      | software-developer       | musician | dressmaker | manager   | dancer   |
| Hobby   | hiking | camping | reading  | rock-climbing | sudoku |

