.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, september, april, january, june
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, hedgehog, guinea-pig, rat
1. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
7. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Birthday   | september  | april    | january | december   | june |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla | guinea-pig    | bird | hedgehog |

