.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
House: modern, farmhouse, colonial, cottage, ranch-style
5 different games are played: poker, chess, billiard, backgammon, mah-jongg
1. the cottage house is the person playing chess##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
4. the ranch-style house is between the farmhouse house and the person playing poker##2
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
8. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| House   | modern | cottage | colonial     | ranch-style     | farmhouse |
| Game     | backgammon   | chess   | poker | billiard | mah-jongg  |

