.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, amaryllis, poppy, aconite
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, grey, ebony, purple
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
5. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
6. the person who likes purple is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
8. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Flower   | dahlia | zinnia | aconite     | amaryllis | poppy |
| Color     | ebony       | green   | grey | blue   | purple        |

