.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, iced-tea, soy-milk, fanta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, action, martial-arts, fantasy, musical
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking cola and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching action movies is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person watching musical movies##2
7. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | iced-tea | sprite | fanta | cola     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | action   | musical       | martial-arts | western |

