3. the ritmeester-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
4. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | adventure      | thriller | spy     | satire      |
| Cigar     | oliveros | ritmeester | old-henry | davidoff | prince |

 